8️⃣ Ideal Trading Session

ES moves most during:

9:30 – 11:30 AM
1:30 – 4:00 PM

Worst time:

11:30 – 1:30 (lunch chop)
9️⃣ Trade Management

Your system is designed for:

Win rate ≈ 35-40%
Reward ≈ 2x risk

That means:

Many small losses
Few big winners

Example sequence:

Loss
Loss
Win
Loss
Win
Win

Still profitable.

🔑 The Core Idea

Your strategy exploits one simple behavior:

Trends
pause
then continue

You enter during the pause.

